{"tid":1632341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開始準備下一個戰場：11月區議會選舉","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:49:11.000Z","uid":123774,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7734a29804b895fc6833f6f33061f927d5854a20","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"無叫大家停止做而家嘅嘢<br />\n但係我哋需要更長遠去準備下一個戰場<br />\n<br />\n雖然現行制度並唔係我哋心目中要求<br />\n但係議席先至係佢哋嘅春袋<br />\n我哋一樣要奉陪到底<br />\n<br />\n唔係袋住先 而係邊打邊袋<br />\n拎返議會否決權返嚟<br />\n等政府唔可以夾硬黎<br />\n<br />\n冷靜啲聽下王喜講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/443089702474133/posts/2382737075176043?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F443089702474133%2Fposts%2F2382737075176043%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEptagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=9298c163\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/443089702474133/posts/2382737075176043?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"453a1312909947ec85474839d3d39d8232638993","tid":1632341,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n仆街政府一定會諗盡辦法取消選舉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1504e2303098c02214e231faf0cfd7112e79980","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:14.000Z","msg":"睇埋陶傑點講<br />\n唔係叫佢做大台<br />\n但有道理嘅說話大家都應該聽一聽<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陶傑：<br />\n午夜旺角，雨中街頭。有如雨果小說和音樂劇「悲慘世界」的街頭抗爭場面。<br />\n<br />\n形勢混亂，顯然有林鄭及其幕後勢力的臥底，混入抗爭對伍中，令暴力不斷升級。<br />\n<br />\n請年輕人現在跟保持冷靜。記着：下一個戰場，是區議會選舉，不是街頭某些商店櫥窗和銀行鐵閘。Be Water，應該柔軟的時候，要柔軟，不必，也不可，時時都維持剛烈。Be courageous, but also be smart ! <br />\n<br />\n願大家平安。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3054742494598253?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F272574169481780%2Fposts%2F3054742494598253%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEptagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=181c4354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/272574169481780/posts/3054742494598253?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"bce0142b9a5bc8dafca28e89bf8ed02d5b00a591","tid":1632341,"uid":246884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:44:19.000Z","msg":"話你知咩叫和勇合一<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630017</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4f45359ca26932d2957d24f4360865ca92ef2cc","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"453a1312909947ec85474839d3d39d8232638993","tid":1632341,"uid":327169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n仆街政府一定會諗盡辦法取消選舉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"係 佢哋絕對係想取消或者延遲<br />\n如果依家出嚟選有人計過投票率到六成<br />\n- 建制派會失去一半議席<br />\n- 特首選委會佢哋會冇100張票<br />\n我唔係好識 無FC"},{"pid":"a322240ffb7b7e00af991264b73301b35d017fda","tid":1632341,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:47:23.000Z","msg":"區選佢一定大敗<br />\n唔好同我講人血慢頭"},{"pid":"7f2cfc1b572283a1f746eefb1a1507afae7f2fc7","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:47:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f1808394591da18417443a3d7d4f67381e5e2fc","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:52:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>連登話準備選舉就係輸嘅人<br />\n就係最驚我哋去投票拉而家建制落嚟嘅人<br />\n<br />\n越近11月24日就會越多呢種人響度出現<br />\n大家記住我哋係要拎返控制權<br />\n<br />\n呢場係持久戰 <br />\n區議會選舉我哋一定要贏</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"605bb267ee365faefad33253570457466dd9ee06","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b400d236ec7a749a3f4a77fd05bd137e847d2a34","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8a4dd91574834c12c96a630269b65e56695f4d2","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:04:00.000Z","msg":"運動到咗第二個樽頸位<br />\n聚焦區議會選舉亦可以令大家搵返Focus"},{"pid":"90a699545f5f1cfb3e26bb280bce4381c15a2b0f","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:06:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9db1eaafa79f614409f040efc14c3b4143e39146","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:07:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49e154aac940e1b353fa90d6385045887755b8f3","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:08:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5338d7ad3f9c1b0b05fb891a51498b16a705804","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:14:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e16f565be60e88331e0d710a43af8a4531b34f3c","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:24:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"277126841a65adbfa7f5d8f471dfdb0b019ea820","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f198bf5d2e0cb299bd3487e9beb88e020c1e44f","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:02:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"539ef53822753640711cc6c239965f7a6d124c3a","tid":1632341,"uid":56166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f1808394591da18417443a3d7d4f67381e5e2fc","tid":1632341,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10